(1157, 1, '2013-02-20 22:38:17', '2013-02-20 22:38:17', '<h2>A complete Array Of Options</h2>\nThe theme comes with a really easy-to-use, versatile options panel. In it you will have access to all the settings controlling the theme\'s behavior, being able to customize them to your liking. We have built the options page with versatility in mind, so it offers a really flexible suite of options.\n<h2>Really Easy To Configure</h2>\nThe options page is really straightforward, and requires to coding at all to get around. All the basic options are toggled with a single click, and each option is descriptive about what it does, and how. Expect no surprises. Your site will be fully functional in a matter of minutes.\n<h2>Full Customization Tools</h2>\nIf you are an advanced user, you\'re in luck! The theme options page also features some more advanced settings that allow you to insert custom CSS and Javascript into de theme. You can perform basic customizations in a matter of seconds and without the need of creating a child theme.', 'Powerful Theme Options', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'open', '', 'powerful-theme-options__trashed', '', '', '2017-07-05 10:20:16', '2017-07-05 10:20:16', '', 885, 'http://demo.cpothemes.com/brilliance/?page_id=1157', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(1162, 1, '2013-02-20 22:46:22', '2013-02-20 22:46:22', '<h2>Google fonts, At Your Service</h2>\nThis theme includes a selection of available fonts directly from Google Webfonts, carefully hand-picked to match with all the possible styles of your site. You can easily change the typefaces of various elements in the design with only a few clicks, and no coding at all. The font selection tool features a small preview that will let you see what each font looks like.\n\nYou can customize the three main typographic elements of this theme:\n\n[list icon="angle-right"]\n<ul>\n	<li>The headings, such as page titles and widget headings</li>\n	<li>The navigation of the main menu</li>\n	<li>The body copy</li>\n</ul>\n[/list]', 'Customizable Typography', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'open', '', 'customizable-typography__trashed', '', '', '2017-07-05 10:20:15', '2017-07-05 10:20:15', '', 885, 'http://demo.cpothemes.com/brilliance/?page_id=1162', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(1166, 1, '2013-02-20 22:52:44', '2013-02-20 22:52:44', '<h2>Adaptable To Any Screen</h2>\nThis theme is responsive! It has been designed from the ground up to adapt to virtually any device screen, ensuring your content will look great no matter where you visit it from. Every element within is made to be flexible, adaptable, and to gracefully degrade on older browsers. Additionally, the theme\'s responsive features can easily be controlled from the theme options page, allowing you to disable them if needed.\n\nIf you wish to, the responsiveness of the theme can be disabled with a simple click. For those who want a more traditional approach to their site, this is a useful option found in the Theme Options page. Doing so will render the site equally on every device at its full resolution.', 'Responsive Design', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'open', '', 'responsive-design__trashed', '', '', '2017-07-05 10:20:17', '2017-07-05 10:20:17', '', 885, 'http://demo.cpothemes.com/brilliance/?page_id=1166', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(1168, 1, '2013-02-20 22:54:32', '2013-02-20 22:54:32', '<h2>WordPress XML File Included</h2>\nWe have bundled all the content featured in this demo in your download package! Using the native WordPress importer, you can recreate all the pages you see featured here in a matter of minutes, being able to work from there onwards.\n<h2>Made For Modifications</h2>\nAdditionally, there are some pages specifically designed to be used as templates. they contain a lot of dummy text for you to fill out, while all the layout and shortcodes are already placed. This way you can achieve stunning, fully customized pages with immersive layouts with only a fraction of the effort.', 'Included Demo Content', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'open', '', 'demo-content__trashed', '', '', '2017-07-05 10:20:15', '2017-07-05 10:20:15', '', 885, 'http://demo.cpothemes.com/brilliance/?page_id=1168', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(1177, 1, '2013-02-20 23:06:14', '2013-02-20 23:06:14', '<h2>Create Immersive Pages With Little Effort</h2>\nThis theme comes with a great variety of custom shortcodes, built with flexibility in mind. With them you can generate compelling and interactive content, all with only a few lines of code directly in the visual post editor. Here are only a few of the shortcodes you can use to create incredible effects:\n\n[column_half]\n\n[list icon="angle-right"]\n<ul>\n	<li>Buttons</li>\n	<li>Messages &amp; Notices</li>\n	<li>Accordions</li>\n	<li>Counters</li>\n	<li>Pricing Tables</li>\n	<li>Google maps</li>\n</ul>\n[/list]\n\n[/column_half][column_half_last]\n\n[list icon="angle-right"]\n<ul>\n	<li>Columns &amp; Full Width Sections</li>\n	<li>Dropcaps</li>\n	<li>Custom lists, like this one</li>\n	<li>Social buttons</li>\n	<li>Mini features</li>\n	<li>Progress Bars</li>\n</ul>\n[/list]\n\n[/column_half_last]', 'Custom Shortcodes', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'open', '', 'custom-shortcodes__trashed', '', '', '2017-07-05 10:20:14', '2017-07-05 10:20:14', '', 885, 'http://demo.cpothemes.com/brilliance/?page_id=1177', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(1182, 1, '2013-02-20 23:38:00', '2013-02-20 23:38:00', '<h2>Full Support suite</h2>\nBuyers get full access to premium support, so you can get your site up and running in no time. We\'ll help you troubleshoot any issue you have during theme installation and setup, and we\'ll guide you through the proper usage of the theme. Furthermore, you can expect to learn a few tricks to get the most out of WordPress!\n<h2>Regular updates And Fixes</h2>\nIn addition to offering premium support, we will also release updates regularly in order to improve the theme. That means it will be thoroughly maintained to ensure there are no issues or problems popping up. Should you find out about a bug, you can notify us and we\'ll investigate into it-- and subsequently releasing an update.', 'Premium Support', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'open', '', 'premium-support__trashed', '', '', '2017-07-05 10:20:17', '2017-07-05 10:20:17', '', 885, 'http://demo.cpothemes.com/brilliance/?page_id=1182', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(1184, 1, '2013-02-20 23:41:01', '2013-02-20 23:41:01', '<h2>Easily Customize The Palette</h2>\nThis theme lets you choose virtually any color scheme for your site, being able to set different tones for both typographic elements and backgrounds. By using the powerful theme options panel, you can accomplish this in just a few clicks, easily changing your site\'s appearance in a few minutes.\n\nThe following elements can be customized using only the Theme Options page:\n<ul>\n	<li>The primary color, which determines the basic color scheme</li>\n	<li>The secondary color, for other minor elements in the layout</li>\n	<li>Heading color, for titles and</li>\n	<li>Navigation color, for the navigation menus</li>\n	<li>Body color, for everything else</li>\n</ul>', 'Unlimited Color Palette', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'open', '', 'unlimited-color-palette__trashed', '', '', '2017-07-05 10:20:18', '2017-07-05 10:20:18', '', 885, 'http://demo.cpothemes.com/brilliance/?page_id=1184', 0, 'page', '', 0),
